{
  "stem": "71.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A young friend of--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wanted to get away from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just could not cope with the situation, with the way of living.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not think that I will be able to-- to adjust to a living like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I also thought that if I go and see how the situation is, like an early bird goes to find a worm, I thought that if I go and I find a way to get my family out.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was not-- yeah, I was 16 when I left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was in end of November.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I just turned 16.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I came to Brest-Litovsk, there were a lot, a lot of people homeless that came.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And somehow we found an older woman with a daughter who had one room, lived in one room.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she rented to us-- to me a cot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I noticed the sign when we went to register, I noticed the sign it says, waitress wanted.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So everybody was-- the whole group that was working, there were laughing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This sign must be from before the war, but I insisted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I want to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the evening when we went, I went back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I found out it was a Turkish konditorei.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was like for Turks that came to Poland and they opened bakeries and like a coffee shop.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when I talk to them, the man started-- you know, I was so young and my hands, he saw that I-- I never did dishes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he tried to discourage me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I persisted that I want to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I got the job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I worked there till the end of December.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I-- I-- I fell from two steps.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
